channel.title: Help Me Please
channel.description: Hi i am new to MoparScape and I wanted to go on peoples runescape private servers i downloaded everything i needed to (as far as i know) MoparScape 3.0 and the latest version of Java. I clicked on the icon "runMoparScape" It started a long load i came back and it said something like "Cannot load title screen" retry in 20 seconds and it did a loop of that over and over. :confused: Could someone please tell me how i can fix this :confused:[br][size=1]Posted at: August 29, 2006, 05:57:15 AM[/size][hr]And if anyone can help me i will offer them a seat of power (Admin Status) on my server should they be interested :D
